/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1889 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:82 */
"VDPCONNECT_NETWORK_UNREACHABLE: The local computer is unable to reach the gateway or the remote computer's network while attempting a connection. This could be due to a network routing issue. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_NETWORK_UNREACHABLE: 尝试连接时，本地计算机无法访问网关或远程计算机网络。这可能是由于网络路由问题所致。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1897 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:84 */
"VDPCONNECT_HOST_UNREACHABLE: The local computer is unable to reach the gateway or the remote computer while attempting a connection. This could be because the gateway or the remote computer is down or not responding. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_HOST_UNREACHABLE: 尝试连接时，本地计算机无法访问网关或远程计算机。这可能是因为网关或远程计算机已关闭或无响应。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1905 */
"VDPCONNECT_HOSTNAME_NOT_RESOLVABLE: The gateway or the remote computer IP address could not be resolvedfor establishing a connection. This could be due to a DNS issue. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_HOSTNAME_NOT_RESOLVABLE: 无法解析网关或远程计算机 IP 地址，从而无法建立连接。这可能是由于 DNS 问题所致。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1912 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:88 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_TIMEDOUT: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer could not be established in a reasonable time period. This could be because the gateway or the remote computer is not reachable, not responding, or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_TIMEDOUT: 无法在合理的时间段内建立与网关或远程计算机的连接。这可能是因为网关或远程计算机无法访问、无响应或者协议服务端口被防火墙阻止。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1921 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:90 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_TERMINATED: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was terminated by the local host networking software. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_TERMINATED: 与网关或远程计算机的连接被本地主机网络软件终止。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1927 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:92 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_RESET: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was reset by the remote host. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_RESET: 与网关或远程计算机的连接被远程主机重置。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1933 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:94 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_ACCESS_DENIED: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was denied access, perhaps by the local host firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_ACCESS_DENIED: 与网关或远程计算机的连接访问被拒绝，可能是由于本地主机防火墙。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1939 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:96 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONN_REFUSED: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer was refused. This could be because the protocol service is not running or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONN_REFUSED: 与网关或远程计算机的连接被拒绝。这可能是因为协议服务未运行或协议服务端口被防火墙阻止。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1947 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:98 */
"VDPCONNECT_CONNECT_TLS: The connection to the gateway or the remote computer could not be established because of a TLS error. This could be due to a TLS handshake failure, a certificate check failure or other related errors. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_CONNECT_TLS: 由于 TLS 错误，无法与网关或远程计算机建立连接。这可能是由于 TLS 握手失败、证书检查失败或其他相关错误所致。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1955 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:100 */
"VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_ERROR: The connection to the remote computer encountered a gateway error. This could be because the agent is not reachable from the gateway or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_ERROR: 与远程计算机的连接遇到网关错误。这可能是因为无法从网关访问代理，或者协议服务端口被防火墙阻止。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1963 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:102 */
"VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_TIMEOUT: The connection to the remote computer encountered a gateway timeout. The gateway could not reach the agent or its connection to the agent was refused because the protocol service is not running or the protocol service port is blocked by a firewall. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_GATEWAY_TIMEOUT: 与远程计算机的连接遇到网关超时。由于协议服务未运行或协议服务端口被防火墙阻止，网关无法访问代理或其与代理的连接被拒绝。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1972 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:104 */
"VDPCONNECT_PEER_UNAVAILABLE: The connection encountered an unavailable peer. This could be because a peer computer, such as a proxy, was unable to handle the connection request. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_PEER_UNAVAILABLE: 连接遇到对等体不可用问题。这可能是因为对等计算机 (如代理) 无法处理连接请求。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

/* File: ../cocoa/cdkVMConnection.m:1979 */
/* File: ../sdk/internal/vdpUtils.cpp:106 */
"VDPCONNECT_PEER_ERROR: The connection encountered a peer error. If the issue persists, please contact your system administrator." = "VDPCONNECT_PEER_ERROR: 连接遇到对等体错误。如果问题仍然存在，请联系您的系统管理员。";

